<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Flame1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Flame,</orth> subst. fire rising from burning bodies: <bibl n="shak. luc 180" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 180</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 1, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.89" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 89</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.2.59" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 2, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.191" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 191</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 1, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.2.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 2, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 138</bibl>. <cit><quote>through fire and through f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 4, 53</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by the f. of yonder glorious heaven,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.6.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 6, 23</bibl></cit>. Plur. <cit><quote>--s:</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 16</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.109" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 109</bibl>. IV Chor. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.109" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 109</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 2, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 5, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.528" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 528</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 167</bibl>. Figuratively used of love: <bibl n="shak. son 109.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 109, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.115.4" default="NO" valid="yes">115, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 191" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 191</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 115</bibl>. <cit><quote>in so true a f. of liking,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.217" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 217</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if I did love you in my master's f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.283" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 283</bibl></cit>. Of passionate desire: <bibl n="shak. luc 6" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.101" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 101</bibl>. Of poetry: <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 23</bibl>. Of ambition. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.328" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 328</bibl>. Of passion: <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 123</bibl>. Of war: H4B Ind. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 123</bibl>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>